  "title": "HR MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>Manage Human Resource management functions (manpower planning, recruitment, on­boarding, training & development, policies review, payroll verification, monthly HR reports etc)</li><li>Oversee and refine employee standards and procedures, using existing HR systems as well as improved or recommended processes</li><li>Recruitment efforts, and prepare employees for their assignments by establishing and conducting orientation and training programs</li><li>Ensure compliance of regulations with CPF, IRAS, MOM, WDA and other agencies</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min 3 years of related working experience in related field is required for this position</li><li>Diploma / Degree in Management</li><li>Prefer working experience in Construction field can commence within short period</li><li>Must be bilingual in English & Mandarin to liaise with Chinese speaking internal/external personnel</li></ul>",
